text.section:
The members of a local team shall be drawn from the following persons, organizations, agencies, and areas of expertise, from within the county, as available:
domestic violence service providers;
law enforcement agencies;
the State's Attorney's office;
the local health department;
the local department of social services;
the domestic violence coordinating council;
batterer intervention services providers;
the Division of Parole and Probation;
hospitals;
judges of the District Court and circuit courts;
clerks of the District Court and circuit courts;
the Chief Medical Examiner's office;
survivors of domestic violence; and
any other person necessary to the work of the local team, recommended by the local team.
